-- Restaurant Group CEO Sees ‘Difficult’ First-Half on Weak Economy
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2012-02-29T08:45:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-29/restaurant-group-ceo-sees-difficult-first-half-on-weak-economy.html
Restaurant Group Plc (RTN)  Chief Executive
Officer Andrew Page says he anticipates a “difficult” first-
half of the year as the U.K. economy remains weak.  “Our feeling is that it will be a pretty difficult first
half of the year,” Page said in a phone interview today. “The
picture should get brighter as we move into the second half.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
